  "description": {
   "en": "A collection of oneshots done by Aono-sensei. There’s various genres covered (Josei, BL, and Yuri) all fitting with the theme of some form of “kindness.”  \n  \n1. An no Niwa:  \nThe story of a terminally ill man and his defective android.  \n  \n2. Futari de Akete:   \nRegarding the friendship of a country boy and the transfer student from the city.  \n  \n3. Kanojo no Hahen:   \nA love triangle formed by an honor student, her male childhood friend, and an unpopular female classmate.  \n  \n3.5. Ame:   \nA weak wizard and a strong witch with a complimentary power.  \n  \n4. After the Fuschia:   \nContinuation of \"Ame.\""
  },
